  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，提升你的技能不是唯一要做的事。在战局中的综合表现才是关键。我有一个小挑战给你，但对你这样的人来说应该不难，对吧？你可以证明自己，使用特定武器完成击杀。我想想，就用5.45x39和7.62x39这俩经典的苏联口径吧。你觉得你能做到吗？",
    "en": "Alright, getting your skills up isnt the only thing that matters. How you perform in raid is the important thing, I got a little challenge for you, but it shouldn't be too difficult for someone like you, right? You can prove it of course, get a few kills with certain weapons. I was thinking about 5.45x39 and 7.62x39, classic soviet firepower. You think you can manage that?"
  },
